data.description: If your buyer is looking for a place to call home, this house has a lot to offer. It is located in the center of Hopewell Twp. close to 376, the airport and 30 mins from Pittsburgh. Clearview Estates is a sidewalk community with a private pool, playgrounds and green space. The house is a solid 3 bedroom brick home with a nice sized yard. The white kitchen has been updated with newer floor covering, new faucet, newer appliances, and  a built-in microwave.  Also, the bathroom has been updated. Underneath the carpet are hardwood floors. The living room has a brand new picture window with a great view of the neighborhood and trees. The basement is wide open and ready to be finished. There is a newer drain system in front of the garage. There is a leased security system in place
